webpackJsonp([0xe04f974558baf800],{"./node_modules/json-loader/index.js!./.cache/json/mathematics-dividing-fractions.json":function(s,i){s.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<h2>Dividing Fractions</h2>\n<p>This is similar to multiplying two fractions, with an additional step</p>\n<p>Consider the expression A ÷ B, here A is called the <i>dividend</i> and B is called the <i>divisor</i>.</p>\n<p>Here are the steps to divide two fractions,</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Take the reciprocal of the divisor fraction (B). </li>\n<li>Multiply the dividend fraction (A) with the reciprocal of the divisor fraction</li>\n<li>Simplify the resultant fraction, if possible</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Examples</h4>\n<h5>Example 1</h5>\n<pre>  <span class="fraction"><sup>2</sup>⁄<sub>3</sub></span> &divide; <span class="fraction"><sup>6</sup>⁄<sub>7</sub></span> </pre>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Take the reciprocal of the divisor. To take a reciprocal of a fraction, interchange the numerator and denominator of that fraction. The reciprocal of <span class="fraction"><sup>6</sup>⁄<sub>7</sub></span> is <span class="fraction"><sup>7</sup>⁄<sub>6</sub></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Multiply the dividend with the reciprocal of the divisor</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre> <span class="fraction"><sup>2</sup>⁄<sub>3</sub></span> &divide; <span class="fraction"><sup>6</sup>⁄<sub>7</sub></span> = <span class="fraction"><sup>2</sup>⁄<sub>3</sub></span> &times; <span class="fraction"><sup>7</sup>⁄<sub>6</sub></span> = <span class="fraction"><sup>7</sup>⁄<sub>9</sub></span> </pre>\n<h5>Example 2</h5>\n<pre>  <span class="fraction"><sup>4</sup>⁄<sub>6</sub></span> &divide; 2 </span> = <span class="fraction"><sup>4</sup>⁄<sub>6</sub></span> &times <span class="fraction"><sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>2</sub></span> = <span class="fraction"><sup>4</sup>⁄<sub>12</sub></span> = <span class="fraction"><sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>3</sub></span> (Simplified) </pre>\n<p>Please note a whole number can be considered as a fraction by considering its denominator as 1.\n<br>Also, you can only divide by non-zero fractions.</p>',fields:{slug:"/mathematics/dividing-fractions/"},frontmatter:{title:"Dividing Fractions"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/mathematics/dividing-fractions/"}}}});
